Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:39.02,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:47.49,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:55.66,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:03.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:10.78,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:21.19,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:30.80,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
